}NowdoSomething()inside offoo.cppis inside theFoonamespace, and thedoSomething()inside ofgoo.cppis inside theGoonamespace. Let’s see what happens when we recompile our program.main.cpp:int doSomething(int x, int y); // forward declaration for doSomething

